sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Boeing topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 9.9%.
Year to date, Boeing has lost about 42.6% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Walmart, trading up 0.3%.
Walmart is showing a gain of 1.3% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble, trading up 0.3%, and Dow, trading up 4.5% on the day.
